    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precision 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, the power is delivered to the tarmac via a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically sound, the vehicle has received vital preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis integrity. The suspension remains tight, preserving the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance that defines this M-division icon.",
