      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior features a sophisticated obsidian black finish that has been regularly waxed; while there are a few minor surface scratches and small chips on the hood consistent with standard road use, the body remains straight and free of any dents. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The pebble-gray leather upholstery is in great shape, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat. All technological features, including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and premium 10-speaker audio system, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the car has been maintained with an open checkbook policy, featuring a complete service log and a brand-new battery installed last quarter. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes provide firm, responsive stopping power. This car drives straight and true, offering a quiet and comfortable ride for its next owner.",
