      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct tactile feedback and control. Critical enthusiast concerns have been addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to prevent floor fatigue, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis maintains its signature 50/50 weight distribution and sharp turn-in. While the exterior displays minor road-wear patina, the powertrain pulls hard to the 8,000 RPM redline without hesitation. The limited-slip differential operates silently, and the braking system has been upgraded with stainless steel lines for improved pedal modulation during spirited driving.",
